values:
hey all havent updated in aaaaaaaages! well my lifes all good at the mo...actually exceptionally happy! more than usual! lol off to brighton 2day with the lovely claire and glan and meg and chris and toby! all fun fun fun!! things going gd with glen yay! been having a rele gd hols actually (no results for lil old me!) should do some coursework but meh! and readings nxt week! im pretty fine and dandy and happy with life.

yep!

hey. 

havent updated in a while. been at laras howse mainly...helpin with the wedding planning and stuff. OMG in a week itll b like...the day of the wedding! AAH! im no longer singing which is kinda good cos i was rele scared. la wanted me to but the organ man broke his ankle or summin. ah well...

so anyway, my week...sunday i went up to (or is it down to? or across to?) maidstone to see aled and jake. went to a party and generally hung then missed my last train so slept at the party place and went to aleds on mon. then i went straight to laras howse and did stuff and erm...quite literlly stayed till wednesday! 

i then went on to a partay thing of mr cheyne's. that was fun except that someone breathed smoke in my face and then i started having an allergy thing and my throat closed up but then i started having a panic attack too so i was breathing rele quickly and shaking and crying and stuff. and i had 5 shots of my ashtma pump when ur only allowed 2. great. billie thought i was gonna die. 

i got home at like 1 and then actually made an appearece at school! amazing i know! as i suspected it was a waste of time and so friday i didnt go in and went to laras instead. HEHE! i was there like all week! the builders all think i live there! one of them asked me if i knew if 'my mum' was home and when me and nathan were fighting kung fu stylee one of them told nathan to be nice to his sister! LMAO! i dnt think i shuld even start talkin bout nathan...

hey all! god i havent updated in aaages. ive been having lots of fun lately on work experience at my drama academy (woo poshness!) where ive been playin with glitter and making scenery and trying on costumes etc. fun fun! 

also been spending lots of time with lara (well, at her howse trying on my dress!) im rele excited now the wedding is like 2 1/2 weeks! omg! im rele scared that i will get rele spotty and look rele bad or loose my voice so i cant sing tho! and omg im sooo nervous about singing! or like wot if i suddenly get well fat and dont fit in my dress? i must remember to invite lots of pple to the evening reception *makes mental note*

also been seeing lots of nathan (cos i now live in their howse!) hehe! omg his friend aled is the most fun person ever! yay! he gonna call me later! woo lots of aled chatting! i love him! i love everyone! including all of u of course! and woo for lu being bk alive! i love u lu! we must catch up over summer! i must catch up with evry1 over summer!

well, love to all! must be off to get all glittery and other fun things with katie! wohoo!

i got an A* in my RE exam! HAHAHAHAHA!! RE is such a fecking joke. no offence to anyone...

im so bored! i have a french oral 2moro and havent revised yet! and i lost the sheets...aagh!and i havent done my media coursework...oh dear! skool is so dull!

im talkin to abby and nathan at the mo. abby is amusing me but nathan is all sad cos nina is online. hmm...he being all ambiguous and crap. he all sad. i dunno if i still like him. i dont no wot is even is about him. i found loadsa stuff that i had like pics of him and us and letters and evrything from when we went out and i remembered loadsa stuff he had sed at the time and i got all sad and stuff and then i felt stupid cos i no its all lies (ie sayin he loves me and im beautiful and blah blah blah..) but i dunno. i love being mates with him tho. bleurg! im such a twat...cos its like i no that he is basically a horny mormon and he dont actually like me cos hey who wuld but i dunno. im dumb and confused and all sad 4 no reason...

hey all. not updated much recently. i keep reading pples updates then going to do mine but i cant b bothered most of the time...go me with my lazyness! well not much has happened this week...got my yr 10 exam results back which were all kinda RELE shit:
english A
media A
french B 
history B
maths B (that is the highest grade 4 that module but i got a low B)
science C/D (i didnt actually read the questions...OOPS!)
 
i like entierly failed! OOPS! anyways, thursday i went to bromley with emma, jon and kaz and bought a PINK bikini and other cool stuff, friday i went put to play footie with some pple and generally muck about, then sat i went to get my ear pierced then met up with abby, sean, pubert etc 4 a bit, then met emma, kaz etc for a bit then met nathan to see MATRIX RELOADED! SUCH a good film! wow! me and nathan had lots of fun as usual with our inuendos. he is my pet tiger...im innocent rele! ;) RELE i am! 

laura was being a bitch as usual this week. she had a majour go at me and it was kinda gettin me down but then i realised that no1 actually likes her, including nathan her apparent 'best friend'. i dont rele care but she just has to make me seem like such a cow...no1 believes her anymore tho. and amy jenkins called me last nite at like midnight after ignoring me for about a month to appologise! that was nice.

and ive been spending lots of time with abby. i love her so much! well thats my life...
i dont like nathan. we r mates and im happy with that! no need to worry! talkin to him now. hes like a best mate, but nuffin more! yaay!

ok im a fucking idiot! why am i such a mongey!?! nathan jst called and sed hes still cut up bout nina and that last nite was cool an all but he thinks nothings changed between us and we are still friends. i had to agree but i let slip that i still love him and so ive sed to sean that i sed that we shuld take a break 4 a while cos i still have strong feelings 4 sum1 else and its not fair.

i wanted something to happen and now i regret it and it made me realise i still love him, but he wants to be friends and he doesnt see that things have changed. why do i always let him do this to me? he always makes me fucking cry. and i hate him for it, but i cant hate him. im so mad at myself. im such a twat.

erm...ok u no that thing i was pissed at myself about a few days ago...um...well something happened about my 'confused feelings'. i kinda have a boyfriend. it isnt sean :S 

i dunno wot it is about said boyfriend but yesterday i kissed him. quite a lot. oops! he was flirtin with me all evenin and stuff just kinda...happened. i still rele like him which is stupid but...i dunno! im confused. hes gonna call me later today. i have no idea wot the situation currently is. i think we r going back out. aagh! help!

ok i think u can all easily guess who im talkin bout rite? evry1 i no is gonna b mad at me! help! hes so...him tho. i thought i was over it, i rele did. but he just made me forget everything he has ever done to hurt me. it all just went away. wot do i do? i wanna get back with him. heeelp!!

ho hum...ive cheered up now. realised i was being a dumbass...as usual! nah im ok now emma will be glad to know!! laras bbq was rele cool. the highlight being when me and billieboo went to sleep in nathans bed and olly came looking for us..hehe bless him! he can drive so good!

yesterday was also cool. after waking up at like 10 at laras and watching mallrats i ventured into beckenham at like 1:30 and went to seans howse. his bed is so comfy. i want to sleep there..mmm...he kept tivkling me tho. went home at like 11:30 oops! his parents are all cheerey! his mum was like 'ur welcome here wenever you want, we wuld b happy to have u!' i dont get it...? why is she mad? someone explain...anyone?

ah well, off out in a bit. yay! dont wanna go back to skool! grr!! i wanna sleep! or be a fish. called flounder. or maybe harold...hmm...
please please ignore those last two entries! im just being a drama queen. its nothin to worry about. rele. im fine. i didnt think when i was writing it. im seriously ok (rele emma! RELE!)

im such a fool

im gonna mess everything up

all because i wanna be 'happy'

ill just be miserable

like everyone else

but no one else is

its just me

i have no will power either. and im eating too much. i dont even know how i feel anymore. im in a wierd mood. i feel sick. maybe i need to be sick. im not gonna have any dinner. im being a drama queen and im keeping everything all bottled up. i cant talk to anyone. my thoughts are all muddled up. i need to be sick.

hmm. holidays are here. been seeing lots of lots of people recently. but its all the same people really. ive been seeing lots of emma, which is always good. i love her so much! we r hoping to have a big park picnic london thing (which will aso hopefully include a tourbus!) with lotsa people. i feel like i havent seen loadsa pple that r rele important to me 4 ages. *sad face*

holidays should be quite gd so far. 2day im going shopping and 2 see the matrix with abby an sean. then theres lotsa stuff with la and billie and on friday im seeing chris, toby, jon, rachel, and maybe serena, luke, oli and toni etc. jst realised u dont no who any of those people are. oops.

so yeh, been feeling quite sad recently really. its like ive seen loads of my friends recently, but i havent seen loads of them as well. theres jst so many important people to me i guess. that didnt make sense.

and oohie!! should hopefully be learnin guitar! my uncle may give me his electric guitar then im gonna get evry1 to teach me 1 song. cool! and luke and dan's bands are both playing at my party! hey its in november but im organised! coolio!

well must be off out. im tired. *sleeps* seeing matrix tho! woo!

brought to you by Quizilla hehehe!! wicked! how i wish that culd b my job! he! omg ultimate coolness!! lara is getting married in 2 months!! yaay! im a bridesmaid of course! made invitations (and cheesecake) yesterday! going dress shopping mon! and then engagement party wed! woo! yay yay yay 4 lara!! and 4 me! bridesmaid!! yaay! i get to help organise everything! and go to the service and the reception (with alcohol! not that i shall drink any!) AND the family reception!! firstly cos im a bridesmaid and secondly cos im laras mlil sister!! woo!!

not at skool all week cos of study leave. but all my exams were last week. im so tired. i went to bed at 4. seans fault. 

(ooh emma...ill explain properly wot the fuck he was going on about last nite wen i talk 2 u next. he was all appologetic bless him! he basically sed he wants to ask me out cos im so great. :) im not gonna argue with that! oh and u r always rite!!)

im bruised from that gig the other day. it was better than i thought. saw quite a few people i new. was cool. the guy in 1 of the bands was talkin to me and megan in the gap between songs and decided to give me his cool orange plectrum for no reason! odd guy! all i need is to learn guitar now...

im going to make cheesecake on thursday with my lala! yay! shuld b fun. gd week planned so far. *smiles*

not rele much 2 say 2day. had exams all week (seriously..every lesson of every day!) only 1 this week on wed and i dont have to go in the rest. seeing emma on friday! yay!

going 2 see sean later *smiles* hes so loovley! then going to a mates gig thing which shuld b quite cool. 2moro doing family crap (after spending the whole week at my grandparents howse). next week im off! yay! was gonna plan stuff but i might jst sleep and stuff. maybe go see billie cos her bdays soon. and i might see sean :)

glad to be home. my room at my grandparents howse still has care bear wallpaper so i got scared. had a nice chat with loadsa people last nite. i was in a wierd mood tho. ah well.

toodles xx

ooh, had the funniest time last nite!! went out with my darling emmas (yes i do mean that as in plural...two people called emma! in one place! confusion!) and had noodley goodness, a walk around bromley, spent 25 minutes trying to send an email on those stupid i plus point things and laughed at some scary 19 yr olds! among other things of course...yay! funfun.

                it is not a rape number!

so anyways, 2day im seeing emma sledge in the evening again (yay!) where i shall kick her ass at bowling, along with my lovely billie boo and some more people. during the day im going to see sean (yes i no, emma and dan are always rite!) which shall be...interesting! lol.

next week i have exams every lesson of every day *cries* and i have all the hard ones in one day. im gonna fail. yes, that was... 
            F
            A
            I
            L

shite. the week after i only have an hour of exams tho. and thats french so itll b piss easy (i hope!) so i basically get a 2 week 1/2 term. wohoo!! im soo scared. im gonna fail. especially media. i have to write an 8 page essay ot summin, learn it then write it from scratch in a 3 hr exam. along wth 2 production pieces. SHIT!! and its on monday *weeps*

ah well. only year 10 exams. they dont matter. right? this time nxt yr i may be suicidal tho :(

must be off to get ready for going out to see sean etc. no idea wots gonna happen. *looks a lil scared* ah well, i can always have jody eh emma!?! ;)  xxx

my name in japenese is Arise Barubara Kennede.

my age in dog years is 105.


thought ud like 2 no...

ooh, and ive got my reading ticket! weekend! hell yeah baby!

la la la! had a quite cool week so far tho it hasnt been too eventful. tues got my hair cut, fuck knows why! it looks SOOOOOO bad!! ah well, itll grow. then i saw billie yesterday!! yay!! her and nathan both said it looks nice which was lovely of them, tho they were probs lieing. and nathan patted me on the head...evil boy! i love billieboo! and her dad gave me a lift home tho there were only 2 spaces (other than his) so billie, glen and i had to kinda all be crushed then i got lost. OOPS!! and me and glen had a conversation bout s club..hehe!

didnt go 2 skool 2day. probably didnt miss much. lala! i shall make an appearence 2moro tho. then sat im off to london hopefully with money to buy stuff...ie clothes. then maybe cinema. and sun i have to work and get money. damn it! and mon theres no skool so i shall be going to the park i think, or bowling with my lovely billieboo. dunno yet.

READINGS SOLD OUT! *cries* i told mum to get my ticket sooner. *cries some more* :(

this has kinda turned all long. oops.

back at skool 2day. it was ok, no real work, plus my form tutors left! yay! period 1 and 2 we had tutorial so we talked, then in history my teacher was off so we talked, and then the work in maths was easy but my class were being slow so i talked and in media we watched a vid, so i talked!!

COOL DAY!! i may fail my exams next year but...oh well! altho if one more person asks me if i have a boyfriend yet i may kill them!!!!! every single person asked the same bloody thing!!!.....

"have u got a new boyfriend yet?"
"nope"
"oh, ok. *sympathetic face* spoken to nathan?"
"yes"
"oh, and hes still with his girlfriend?...blah blah blah"

im like, i went out with him months ago!!!!! and i can cope without a boyfriend! 1/2 of them dont have boyfriends but still feel the need to give me sympathy!! it just pisses me off! i can cope without a love life u no!!! and im over nathan!! ah well... 

just one thought tho, do i rele seem so crap that i cant cope without a boyfriend? everyone seems to think that i need one or ill be like all suicidal! and they all seem to think that cos i dont no anyone i like im obviously in love with mormon boy. and me being friends with him is of course a sign of love.

AAARGHH!!!!! I WILL KILL ONE OF THEM!!!!!

ooh, getting my hair cut 2moz tho!! :D

hey all. i got a free easter egg wih a jungle book 2 book worth 2 pound 50 (the pound button doesnt work!) from the mormon church yesterday! wicked! 

ah, free mormon chocolate! its all good. well, other than the mormon bit rele. lol. and i made friends with this girl who i thought hated me who thought i hated her because it was confusing! but shes SO nice! and i majourly confused nathan like SO much!!! hehe! it was rele fun! good day yesterday! and lots of billie! YAY YAY YAY!!

thats all rele, no actual point other than gloating bout my free mormon choccie! oh, and today i went to the park and attempted to play footie with loadsa mates. it was funny. i should do it more often. im crap tho. and i got home like an hour late so forgot to fone mormon boy. lol.

im going to brighton 2moro!!

ive now done 21 pages of my 30 page art project. blah. cant be bothered anymore. ive been working ALL day. well, didnt get up till 10 cos i had a 2 hour txt war with tom from about midnight to 2am! oops! plus my AMY is home!! YAYNESS!!

im quite proud that ive done so much. i havent done enough yet but chagall is quite boring. im going to make a window tomoro which is quite cool tho.

then i have plans for the rest of my hols! yay! 2moro afternoon im going to the cinema with billieboo and then thursday i going to the park with sean etc and then fri brighton 4 claires bday and sunday im goin riding.

those of u that are observant will have noticed no plans for sat.  im meant to be seeing nathan but i no that wont happen cos well...hes crap rele and will cancel. oh well.

i have so much work still tho! i feel like ive workd loads and i no ive done loads but i have so much left! i still have 1/2 of my english essay and 1/2 of my media and the rest of my art and to finish my other art project and to do my FULLY RENDERED A1 drawing for graphics. AAAGH!! shit. should go do some i guess. *cries*
yay!! tom, emma rose and tammi are talking to me!! and lara!

im bored!! just got home, went to see fone booth. the film that is, not an actual fone booth. even im not that sad, altho i saw a few on the way! lol. was meant to see bulletproof monk but we missed it cos amy and claire were late. its cool tho, fone booth is well good. not what i expected at all but it messed with my brain a bit and i wierdly like films that do that. id recomend seeing it!

anyway, amys in paris (got a txt today, look at her being able to txt from abroad!!) and dads staying at his brothers so its just me and mum. weve bonded a lot which is nice, i dont rele feel like i can talk to her usually but its cool at the moment. and shes letting me do stuff i usually cant like go online a lot and use the fone whenever and stuff.

but alas no one is bloody online!! selfish gimps all of you! well, this annoying girl liz from my skool is and this scary guy called sean and dan, but hes away. so i am spending my time boring u all instead.

i had a chat with will yesterday which was rele nice, havent spoken to him in a while. i was having a low self esteem moment and he just rele cheered me up as usual. he just said some rele nice things *smiles* its nice to know someone cares i guess. thanks will!

and seeing nathan the other day helped me realise a few things, which is cool. i wont bore u all with the details but i was chatting to will (altho he did disagree with most of my arguments!) and it all just made me, i dunno...not *realise* rele but more confirm that i dont like him *in that way* anymore. its cool tho, were friends which is nice.

so stuffs going well rele. god, i cant believe ive only just fully realised that im *over* nathan! its ridiculous!! oh well, im just over emotional and romantic and crap. thanks again to will, u probably didnt mean it and i no im making a big deal but that was like one of the nicest things anyones ever said to me! *smiles*

so yeah, im kinda at peace with myself for once. shocking i no! its nice catching up with people i guess. like i had a huge chat with nathan, who i can just talk about anything with and one with will who just makes me smile when im down and who i love to pieces! plus me and claire had such a laugh today. its all good!

this is a kinda long rant! bbye...

its too early. i have too much homework. and even more coursework. it all sucks. this time next year and the year after and the year after i will be revising. and then ill b revising at uni. the i will be a work. why???? its not fair!!

i think i should go back to primary school. me and tom were discussing this yesterday. start again at nursery, but already know everything i do now. it would be fun!! then u get to the end of year 6 and go back again!! cool! 

i should go and do work. ive just spend like an hour doing art researcheyesk coursework and i did like 8 pages but didnt save as i was going along then my dumbass computer crashed. aaaaaaaaaagggghhhhh!!!!! someone is going to die!

la de da!! noone else will no wot im going on about except dan, and maybe will and emma, and several people...but ANYWAY...

laura has a boyfriend! he is called doug and lives in devon. he looks like a less attractive and entierly unsexy version of bloody brian molko!! they have not met as far as i no, as they met thru the internet. hmmm...

HAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAAAAAAA!!!!!!! if i could post pictures i would, but alas no. sorry!! HAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAAAAAAA!!!!!!! noone else will find this funny....please tell me if u do!!

well, must go laugh some more...hahaha!! also, apparently nathan is irritating her and thats y they are not so close or something. maybe hes annoying her cos he has a girlfriend!!

ah! u no u r truly over crappy arguments when u can laugh hysterically at the person involved!!

NO MORE SCHOOL!!!!!! yay!! three of my friends got sent home from skool early 4 drinking alcohol at skool. hehe. i got attacked by some guy climing to be in love with me on my way home. help!! oh well. more fun to come...

bloody hell! all of my last updates have said theyre at like 5am cos my mums mucked up the time on the compluter and wont let me change it back for some reason. grrr!! *looks angry and shakes fist at mother*

im not actually THAT wierd, i dont wake up at that time rele! honest. nearly chocolate times!! hehe, i shouldnt eat too much or ill get fat. oh well. im gonna get hit for saying that.

im gonna go and write a thing for amys dt coursework being alice watson now. ho hum.

ps. isnt satong a cool word!!??!!

my god, just remembered that theres a film out soon called BULLET PROOF MONK!!!! wicked! and the slogan is like A MONK. A PUNK. A CHICK. A KICK-ASS FLICK! cool!!!

i got 100% on my first bit of french coursework. yay me!! hehe. only 1 more day!! yay yay yay!!

ho hum...had the FUNNIEST history lesson 2day!! we're learnin bout like living condidions  in like 1850 and we have to do a shitty role play but our group have to do a comedy theme so were like killing the tax inspector and the village idiot decides that we shuld bury him in the mountin of crap (MOUNT SHITTERIST!!) so we all climb it and fall down and die from smell etc

it was just well funny and me and rhiannon were in hysterics!! its gonna be soooo funny when we perform it!!

just watched the truman show. i really like the idea of that film. although its not as extreme in most peoples cases, i think that the general message is true for everyone. its like u live ur life as a child and everything seems to revolve around you. but as u get older u loose that feeling and other people are introduced into your 'show' that you care about and they slowly come and go. and at the same time you are introduced into other peoples 'shows' and u become important to them. then after a while you realise that u are actually really insignificant in the world in general and that the point of your existence is to entertain other people. 

thats how i see it anyway.

mummy day today. got mum a dull book about teaching with the word gorilla in the title and some mr men chocolate from thorntons. she was happy. good good.

mummy bought me the matrix. mmmm...keanu reeves!! also, i bought the new placebo album!! YAY!! have until tuesday to listen to it and then im leanding it to dan cos im nice. also in an effort to prevent him from buying and making me use a certain object because that is just plain wrong. WRONG!!i think dan will agree with me. hehe 

will is mean. the man told me to get that train. im not just stupid. he lied to me. he wanted me to get lost. it wasnt my fault!! EVIL man!! like the evil ticket inspector that told me to lie convincingly. theyre all bastards. evil bastards. yes.


the only thing you can rely on 
is that you cant rely on anything
dont go and sell your soul for self-esteem
dont be plasticine


im going to go and have some breakfast now. ho hum.
ooooh, also just remembered...nathan has FINALLY realised that laura is in love with him!! hahaha!! hes so slow!! none of u no wot im on about but i find it funny...

lalala!! good morning all!! mummy day 2moro. poo. havent bought present yet. ooops!

just realised how much of a cow i sounded in the last entry. its none of my buisness who nathan goes out with and im all like 'i dont think i have a problem with it'. im such a cow. oh well. hehe

blah blah blah. im bored. should do some homework. shit. oh well. i dont like work. im going to stop boring you all now...

brought to you by Quizilla Hell yeah!! those quizes(?)are accurate!!! how do u spell the plural of quiz? i had such a cool day!! yayness!! stayed at laras howse and nathan was out which was really cool cos didnt wanna see him. he is going out with nina but im cool with it i guess. ill probably realise that im not in a few days, but im pretty sure im over him now. much thanks to my dearest dans horny mormon comments i think! i really wanna say thanx 2 everyone cos i no ive been a pain recently and so thanks for putting up with me and listening to me cry or wotever! and im not saying that i dont appreciate u all but i think dan does deserve a special mention. anyway...then got up at 5 45 after going to bed at like 3 and got a bus with tricia. all good!! then i asked the guy at orpington station which train went to kent house and he said the 7 47 on plat 1 so i go there and get on the train just before it pulls out. THEN it pulls out and says that it goes to shortlands then fast to catford...panick!! so i get off at shortlands with the intention of getting a 227 to skool and who do i see at the station? one of my favouritest people in the world...DAN!! he greets me with 'wot r u doing here, u dont live here!!' and i chatter to him and explain myself. then i scared amy, will etc on the train by grinning as i walked past!! plus confused them i think! hehe!! and my bus came straight away and i saw my friend paul. i was in SUCH a good mood at skool!! it was just really cool cos i saw lots of people and generally had yayness!! so, yeah im happy at the moment. plus, im a pink lady!! hehe. much love to all...

ooooh, just bin on the fone to my lovely bridesmaid and had an uber cool idea...in eatster there shuld b a mass bowlage or ice skating trip or sumfin!! it wuld b mega coolness!!

so if sumone wants to invite themselves and give me some idea of wot to do who 2 invite and when etc then i can get organising!! yay!!
